{"id":869,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":869,"title":"Ezekiel 41","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 41"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel sees the inner temple and the Holy of Holies, and he is shown their form and size."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.1","order":"02.27.041.58207"},["b","1"],"Afterward he brought me to the temple, and measured the posts, six cubits broad on the one side, and six cubits broad on the other side,",["i","which was"],"the breadth of the tabernacle."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.2","order":"02.27.041.58208"},["b","2"],"And the breadth of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"door"],["i","was"],"ten cubits; and the sides of the door",["i","were"],"five cubits on the one side, and five cubits on the other side: and he measured the length thereof, forty cubits: and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"breadth"],", twenty cubits."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.3","order":"02.27.041.58209"},["b","3"],"Then went he inward, and measured the post of the door, two cubits; and the door, six cubits; and the breadth of the door, seven cubits."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.4","order":"02.27.041.58210"},["b","4"],"So he measured the length thereof, twenty cubits; and the breadth, twenty cubits, before the temple: and he said unto me, This",["i","is"],"the most",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"holy",["i","place"]],["i","."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.5","order":"02.27.041.58211"},["b","5"],"After he measured the wall of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"house"],", six cubits; and the breadth of",["i","every"],"side chamber, four cubits, round about the house on every side."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.6","order":"02.27.041.58212"},["b","6"],"And the side chambers",["i","were"],"three, one over another, and thirty in order; and they entered into the wall which",["i","was"],"of the house for the side",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"chambers"],"round about, that they might have hold, but they had not hold in the wall of the house."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.7","order":"02.27.041.58213"},["b","7"],"And",["i","there was"],"an enlarging, and a winding about still upward to the side chambers: for the winding about of the house went still upward round about the house: therefore the breadth of the house",["i","was still"],"upward, and so increased",["i","from"],"the lowest",["i","chamber"],"to the highest by the midst."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.8","order":"02.27.041.58214"},["b","8"],"I saw also the height of the house round about: the foundations of the side chambers",["i","were"],"a full reed of six great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"cubits"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.9","order":"02.27.041.58215"},["b","9"],"The thickness of the wall, which",["i","was"],"for the side chamber without,",["i","was"],"five cubits: and",["i","that"],"which",["i","was"],"left",["i","was"],"the place of the side chambers that",["i","were"],"within."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.10","order":"02.27.041.58216"},["b","10"],"And between the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"chambers"],["i","was"],"the wideness of twenty cubits round about the house on every side."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.11","order":"02.27.041.58217"},["b","11"],"And the doors of the side chambers",["i","were"],"toward",["i","the place that was"],"left, one door toward the north, and another door toward the south: and the breadth of the place that was left",["i","was"],"five cubits round about."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.12","order":"02.27.041.58218"},["b","12"],"Now the building that",["i","was"],"before the separate place at the end toward the west",["i","was"],"seventy cubits broad; and the wall of the building",["i","was"],"five cubits thick round about, and the length thereof ninety cubits."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.13","order":"02.27.041.58219"},["b","13"],"So he measured the house, an hundred cubits long; and the separate place, and the building, with the walls thereof, an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"hundred"],"cubits long;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.14","order":"02.27.041.58220"},["b","14"],"Also the breadth of the face of the house, and of the separate place toward the east, an hundred cubits."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.15","order":"02.27.041.58221"},["b","15"],"And he measured the length of the building",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"over against"],"the separate place which",["i","was"],"behind it, and the galleries thereof on the one side and on the other side, an hundred cubits, with the inner temple, and the porches of the court;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.16","order":"02.27.041.58222"},["b","16"],"The door posts, and the narrow windows, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"galleries"],"round about on their three stories, over against the door,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"ceiled"],"with wood round about, and from the ground up to the windows, and the windows",["i","were"],"covered;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.17","order":"02.27.041.58223"},["b","17"],"To that above the door, even unto the inner house, and without, and by all the wall round about within and without, by measure."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18","order":"02.27.041.58224"},["b","18"],"And",["i","it was"],"made with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"cherubims"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"palm"],"trees, so that a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"palm"],"tree",["i","was"],"between a cherub and a cherub; and",["i","every"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"cherub"],"had two faces;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.19","order":"02.27.041.58225"},["b","19"],"So that the face of a man",["i","was"],"toward the palm tree on the one side, and the face of a young lion toward the palm tree on the other side:",["i","it was"],"made through all the house round about."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.20","order":"02.27.041.58226"},["b","20"],"From the ground unto above the door",["i","were"],"cherubims and palm trees made, and",["i","on"],"the wall of the temple."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.21","order":"02.27.041.58227"},["b","21"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"posts"],"of the temple",["i","were"],"squared,",["i","and"],"the face of the sanctuary; the appearance",["i","of the one"],"as the appearance",["i","of the other."]],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.22","order":"02.27.041.58228"},["b","22"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"altar"],"of wood",["i","was"],"three cubits high, and the length thereof two cubits; and the corners thereof, and the length thereof, and the walls thereof,",["i","were"],"of wood: and he said unto me, This",["i","is"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"table"],"that",["i","is"],"before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.23","order":"02.27.041.58229"},["b","23"],"And the temple and the sanctuary had two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"doors"],"."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.24","order":"02.27.041.58230"},["b","24"],"And the doors had two leaves",["i","apiece,"],"two turning leaves; two",["i","leaves"],"for the one door, and two leaves for the other",["i","door."]],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.25","order":"02.27.041.58231"},["b","25"],"And",["i","there were"],"made on them, on the doors of the temple, cherubims and palm trees, like as",["i","were"],"made upon the walls; and",["i","there were"],"thick",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"planks"],"upon the face of the porch without."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.26","order":"02.27.041.58232"},["b","26"],"And",["i","there were"],"narrow windows and palm trees on the one side and on the other side, on the sides of the porch, and",["i","upon"],"the side chambers of the house, and thick planks."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.2a","order":"02.27.041.58233"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/47.1"},"Ezek. 47:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.2b","order":"02.27.041.58235"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.2"},"1 Kgs. 6:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.4a","order":"02.27.041.58237"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.16"},"1 Kgs. 6:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.13"},"Ezek. 44:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/45.3"},"45:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.39"},"D&C 124:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.5a","order":"02.27.041.58239"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"temple."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.6a","order":"02.27.041.58241"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.5.5,8"},"1 Kgs. 6:5 (5, 8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.8a","order":"02.27.041.58243"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.5"},"Ezek. 40:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.13"},"43:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.10a","order":"02.27.041.58245"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.17"},"Ezek. 40:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.4.1,4-5"},"42:4 (1, 4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.13a","order":"02.27.041.58247"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.47"},"Ezek. 40:47"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.8"},"42:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.15a","order":"02.27.041.58249"},["b","15a"],["span.small","OR"],"facing or opposite."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.16a","order":"02.27.041.58251"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.3"},"Ezek. 42:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.16b","order":"02.27.041.58253"},["b","16b"],["span.small","HEB"],"paneled or veneered."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18a","order":"02.27.041.58255"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.29.29,32,35"},"1 Kgs. 6:29 (29, 32, 35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.36"},"7:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18b","order":"02.27.041.58257"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.9"},"Rev. 7:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18c","order":"02.27.041.58259"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.16"},"Ezek. 40:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18d","order":"02.27.041.58261"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.14"},"Ezek. 10:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.21a","order":"02.27.041.58263"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/46.2"},"Ezek. 46:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.22a","order":"02.27.041.58265"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.1"},"Ex. 30:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/11.1"},"Rev. 11:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.22b","order":"02.27.041.58267"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.16"},"Ezek. 44:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.12.7,12"},"Mal. 1:12 (7, 12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.23a","order":"02.27.041.58269"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.31.31-33"},"1 Kgs. 6:31 (31–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.25a","order":"02.27.041.58271"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.6"},"1 Kgs. 7:6"],"."]]}
